# Appid CLI Configuration
#
# Choose ONE of the following modes:

# API Mode - Connect to running JWT application
# The application must have jwt.appid-key.api-enabled=true
BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080

# YAML Mode - Directly modify application.yml file
# APP_PATH=../jwt-core

# Notes:
# - API mode requires the JWT application to be running
# - YAML mode requires the jwt-core project to be accessible
# - Only ONE mode should be active at a time
